I"å<p>Not 1/6<sup>th</sup> of the way in to <a href="/2018/11/Almost-NaNoWriMo.html">Almost NaNoWriMo</a>, and I‚Äôll admit to feeling a little defensive. I was originally thinking of this article this morning in terms of being a spot-check or reflection on the exercise so far, but if I‚Äôm being brutally honest, it was a couple of comments that have been on a slow burn in the back of my mind since last night:
<!--more--></p>
